title: PES 2014 Ps3 _DATA_PACK_2.0
description:
* GAME ID : = BLES01930 || BLUS31322


* Data Pack ver. := 2.0


* Install Guide : = First Install Update patch according to ur game id

              
Second copy data pack file to dev hdd0/game/BLES01930_DATAPACK OR BLUS31322_DATAPACK 

Third Go to Recovery Menu Select Rebuild Database ... tht's it.. you've done evrythin
